OL,6,FMeanwhile, the National Union of
OL,7,FJournalists' cross-party Parliamentary
OL,8,FGroup is going to meet Ofcom
OL,9,Frepresentatives later this month to
OL,10,Fdiscuss planned and implemented cuts.
OL,12,FOn the agenda will be the plans for
OL,13,Flocal radio, the closure of local TV in
OL,14,FCambridge and Oxford, the axing of the
OL,15,FBBC Radio Foyle Breakfast Show and the
OL,16,Fclosure of the BBC News Channel and BBC
OL,17,FWorld News, in favour of a combined
OL,18,Fnews channel for audiences around the
OL,19,Fworld and the UK.
OL,3,CUK versus the World (Service): BBC
OL,4,Cchair calls for funding switch
