PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F343A1674477840
OL,6,FThe NUJ says Ofcom will be asked about
OL,7,Fthe impact of these measures on
OL,8,Faudiences and what Ofcom should be
OL,9,Fdoing to protect public service
OL,10,Fbroadcasting and the provision of news
OL,11,Fand current affairs by the BBC.
OL,13,FThe most recent rounds of cuts to BBC
OL,14,Fservices have taken place with little
OL,15,For no consultation. What information
OL,16,Fhas been shared has been mostly
OL,17,Fhigh-level, with a more detailed
OL,18,Fbreakdown missing.
