OL,6,FA number of commercial broadcasters are
OL,7,Funderstood to be unhappy with the way
OL,8,Fthe BBC is requesting reductions or
OL,9,Fremovals of quotas.
OL,11,FChanges have been implemented with
OL,12,Flittle or no notice. The BBC declined
OL,13,Fto publish updated schedules showing
OL,14,Fwhat would replace The Papers on the
OL,15,FNews Channel until the day after the
OL,16,Flast edition aired.
